saṃyutta nikāya 1
3. sattivagga
21. sattisutta
sāvatthinidānaṃ.
ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho sā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:
“sattiyā viya omaṭṭho,
ḍayhamānova matthake;
kāmarāgappahānāya,
sato bhikkhu paribbaje”ti.
“sattiyā viya omaṭṭho,
ḍayhamānova matthake;
sakkāyadiṭṭhippahānāya,
sato bhikkhu paribbaje”ti.
